[
  {
    "text": "It's a boy.",
    "start": 38.527,
    "duration": 1.311
  },
  {
    "text": "Congratulations.",
    "start": 41.114,
    "duration": 1.541
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi there.",
    "start": 43.92,
    "duration": 1.423
  },
  {
    "text": "He's beautiful.",
    "start": 46.21,
    "duration": 1.397
  },
  {
    "text": "He's going to do \ngreat things.",
    "start": 48.27,
    "duration": 2.261
  },
  {
    "text": "I just know it.",
    "start": 51.194,
    "duration": 1.219
  },
  {
    "text": "Happy Birthday, David!",
    "start": 52.897,
    "duration": 2.068
  },
  {
    "text": "We love you.",
    "start": 55.884,
    "duration": 1.264
  },
  {
    "text": "More global meteor strikes reported recently,",
    "start": 57.791,
    "duration": 2.71
  },
  {
    "text": "as \ntop Friend Industries scientists",
    "start": 60.501,
    "duration": 2.096
  },
  {
    "text": "race to find a solution",
    "start": 62.597,
    "duration": 1.578
  },
  {
    "text": "to the absence of Jupiter's...",
    "start": 64.175,
    "duration": 1.446
  },
  {
    "text": "We're nearly there.",
    "start": 65.621,
    "duration": 1.232
  },
  {
    "text": "Happy Birthday, Master David.",
    "start": 135.232,
    "duration": 2.154
  },
  {
    "text": "Ew.",
    "start": 149.44,
    "duration": 0.635
  },
  {
    "text": "Get away from me, you freak.",
    "start": 150.279,
    "duration": 1.831
  },
  {
    "text": "Earth needs Heroes.",
    "start": 162.061,
    "duration": 1.939
  },
  {
    "text": "And that hero could be you!",
    "start": 164.0,
    "duration": 2.491
  },
  {
    "text": "So join the StarGoose program",
    "start": 166.491,
    "duration": 2.436
  },
  {
    "text": "and become the great hero \nthat you were destined to be!",
    "start": 168.927,
    "duration": 3.61
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey there, Legolas.",
    "start": 174.424,
    "duration": 1.985
  },
  {
    "text": "You need legs, kid!",
    "start": 179.879,
    "duration": 1.985
  },
  {
    "text": "My son.",
    "start": 183.472,
    "duration": 1.496
  },
  {
    "text": "You were always destined for great things.",
    "start": 185.249,
    "duration": 3.339
  },
  {
    "text": "I love you.",
    "start": 189.433,
    "duration": 2.172
  },
  {
    "text": "Citizen!",
    "start": 210.584,
    "duration": 0.894
  },
  {
    "text": "Need a friend?",
    "start": 212.013,
    "duration": 1.671
  },
  {
    "text": "Reverse! Turn around!",
    "start": 235.0,
    "duration": 2.404
  },
  {
    "text": "What the bloody hell is \nthat?",
    "start": 237.76,
    "duration": 2.243
  },
  {
    "text": "We got another one!",
    "start": 245.643,
    "duration": 1.628
  },
  {
    "text": "Abandon ship!",
    "start": 248.869,
    "duration": 1.106
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh my god!",
    "start": 255.33,
    "duration": 1.165
  },
  {
    "text": "This wasn't part of the deal!",
    "start": 256.495,
    "duration": 2.064
  },
  {
    "text": "Screw \nthis!",
    "start": 258.559,
    "duration": 1.125
  },
  {
    "text": "Aborting mission.",
    "start": 259.684,
    "duration": 1.207
  },
  {
    "text": "Getting the hell outta here.",
    "start": 260.891,
    "duration": 1.746
  },
  {
    "text": "My legs!",
    "start": 275.0,
    "duration": 1.066
  },
  {
    "text": "Help me!",
    "start": 277.367,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "Those things are distracted.",
    "start": 308.707,
    "duration": 1.665
  },
  {
    "text": "We need to keep moving now!",
    "start": 310.372,
    "duration": 2.509
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 312.881,
    "duration": 0.936
  },
  {
    "text": "And how to you propose \nthat?",
    "start": 313.817,
    "duration": 1.824
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you going to give us a ride?",
    "start": 315.641,
    "duration": 2.154
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, you wanna go do ya?",
    "start": 318.498,
    "duration": 1.739
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll kick you re arse right \nhere!",
    "start": 320.237,
    "duration": 2.137
  },
  {
    "text": "Sorry for the delay.",
    "start": 323.833,
    "duration": 1.231
  },
  {
    "text": "I will lure that Moon Titan",
    "start": 325.906,
    "duration": 1.486
  },
  {
    "text": "towards Dr. Chen s facility.",
    "start": 327.392,
    "duration": 1.805
  },
  {
    "text": "I suggest \nhitching a ride.",
    "start": 329.58,
    "duration": 1.757
  },
  {
    "text": "Those things have names?",
    "start": 332.459,
    "duration": 1.699
  },
  {
    "text": "Well. Let's get going.",
    "start": 338.993,
    "duration": 2.408
  },
  {
    "text": "It's on the move!",
    "start": 367.689,
    "duration": 1.386
  },
  {
    "text": "Hold on!",
    "start": 369.713,
    "duration": 1.139
  },
  {
    "text": "It's working!\nIt's following the FriendBot.",
    "start": 376.414,
    "duration": 2.727
  },
  {
    "text": "Did you change to grip tires, \nwheel boy?",
    "start": 379.515,
    "duration": 2.303
  },
  {
    "text": "Shut your mouth!",
    "start": 382.456,
    "duration": 1.128
  },
  {
    "text": "Bloody hell. This thing is fast.",
    "start": 384.094,
    "duration": 3.073
  },
  {
    "text": "We are at now at a reachable \ndistance.",
    "start": 388.035,
    "duration": 2.296
  },
  {
    "text": "Please disembark the Moontitan.",
    "start": 390.331,
    "duration": 2.431
  },
  {
    "text": "How the hell are we supposed to do that?",
    "start": 393.119,
    "duration": 1.938
  },
  {
    "text": "Improvise.",
    "start": 395.618,
    "duration": 1.067
  },
  {
    "text": "Crap!",
    "start": 403.063,
    "duration": 0.863
  },
  {
    "text": "Brace for impact!",
    "start": 405.584,
    "duration": 1.457
  },
  {
    "text": "Jeez. I made it!",
    "start": 412.142,
    "duration": 1.926
  },
  {
    "text": "I didn't die!",
    "start": 414.068,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "Unfortunately.",
    "start": 415.751,
    "duration": 1.481
  },
  {
    "text": "Gnosis 9 is right ahead.",
    "start": 417.232,
    "duration": 1.903
  },
  {
    "text": "We should hurry.",
    "start": 419.135,
    "duration": 1.106
  },
  {
    "text": "Dr. Chen needs us.",
    "start": 420.241,
    "duration": 1.65
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's get going.",
    "start": 424.494,
    "duration": 1.636
  },
  {
    "text": "Moonbeasts! 4 o clock.",
    "start": 435.749,
    "duration": 2.352
  },
  {
    "text": "Cannon boy! \nQuick!",
    "start": 438.56,
    "duration": 1.479
  },
  {
    "text": "Shoot another bubblegum!",
    "start": 440.039,
    "duration": 1.626
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, we're screwed.",
    "start": 445.122,
    "duration": 1.598
  },
  {
    "text": "You were always destined \nfor great things.",
    "start": 448.816,
    "duration": 3.355
  },
  {
    "text": "Get to Dr. Chen.",
    "start": 452.852,
    "duration": 1.499
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll hold them off.",
    "start": 454.632,
    "duration": 1.451
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you crazy?",
    "start": 456.517,
    "duration": 1.674
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't be a hero, wheel boy.",
    "start": 458.191,
    "duration": 1.789
  },
  {
    "text": "You won't survive.",
    "start": 460.184,
    "duration": 1.537
  },
  {
    "text": "I've made a lot of mistakes in my life.",
    "start": 461.913,
    "duration": 2.439
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll say.",
    "start": 464.352,
    "duration": 1.138
  },
  {
    "text": "But now...\nIt's time I do something good.",
    "start": 465.49,
    "duration": 2.903
  },
  {
    "text": "Now go!",
    "start": 468.52,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "You made it.",
    "start": 497.028,
    "duration": 0.939
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank God.",
    "start": 497.967,
    "duration": 1.102
  },
  {
    "text": "Listen, there's no \ntime.",
    "start": 499.069,
    "duration": 2.074
  },
  {
    "text": "The attack on my lab wasn't random.",
    "start": 501.628,
    "duration": 1.998
  },
  {
    "text": "I found out what they re doing.",
    "start": 503.626,
    "duration": 1.965
  },
  {
    "text": "Anyone exposed \nto high levels of Moonjuice.",
    "start": 505.591,
    "duration": 2.991
  },
  {
    "text": "Soldiers, workers, survivors...",
    "start": 508.582,
    "duration": 2.076
  },
  {
    "text": "They're being harvested.",
    "start": 511.117,
    "duration": 1.421
  },
  {
    "text": "For something called Project Phobos.",
    "start": 512.538,
    "duration": 2.894
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not just the Umbra Zone.",
    "start": 516.3,
    "duration": 1.453
  },
  {
    "text": "There's a reason \nthe entire planet runs on moonjuice.",
    "start": 517.753,
    "duration": 3.467
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not just an energy source.",
    "start": 521.679,
    "duration": 1.946
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a fertilizer!",
    "start": 523.957,
    "duration": 1.676
  },
  {
    "text": "We need to stop-",
    "start": 525.633,
    "duration": 0.906
  },
  {
    "text": "Objective updated.",
    "start": 526.539,
    "duration": 1.246
  },
  {
    "text": "Dr. Chen, terminated.",
    "start": 528.659,
    "duration": 1.457
  },
  {
    "text": "I specifically gave the order",
    "start": 539.567,
    "duration": 1.854
  },
  {
    "text": "to leave this one unharmed!",
    "start": 541.421,
    "duration": 1.838
  },
  {
    "text": "He's one of our greatest hybrid assets!",
    "start": 543.667,
    "duration": 2.679
  },
  {
    "text": "Ugh... Well...",
    "start": 547.365,
    "duration": 1.457
  },
  {
    "text": "at least his blood will be put to good use.",
    "start": 549.026,
    "duration": 2.859
  },
  {
    "text": "And just in time.",
    "start": 552.616,
    "duration": 1.747
  },
  {
    "text": "As news \nemerges of more survivors",
    "start": 561.124,
    "duration": 2.666
  },
  {
    "text": "being rescued from the Umbra Zone",
    "start": 563.79,
    "duration": 1.903
  },
  {
    "text": "and given safe refuge,",
    "start": 565.693,
    "duration": 1.636
  },
  {
    "text": "the world turns its gratitude",
    "start": 567.655,
    "duration": 1.725
  },
  {
    "text": "to Friend Industries,",
    "start": 569.38,
    "duration": 1.657
  },
  {
    "text": "who are forever at the forefront",
    "start": 571.037,
    "duration": 1.918
  },
  {
    "text": "of making our \nworld and beyond",
    "start": 572.955,
    "duration": 2.488
  },
  {
    "text": "a better place for humanity.",
    "start": 575.443,
    "duration": 2.385
  },
  {
    "text": "Whatever the cost.",
    "start": 578.619,
    "duration": 1.706
  },
  {
    "text": "In other headlines,",
    "start": 589.308,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "global authorities have suspended",
    "start": 590.542,
    "duration": 2.246
  },
  {
    "text": "all non-essential travel to Mars.",
    "start": 592.788,
    "duration": 2.361
  },
  {
    "text": "Vacationers are now encouraged",
    "start": 595.353,
    "duration": 2.161
  },
  {
    "text": "to consider Venus.",
    "start": 597.514,
    "duration": 1.273
  },
  {
    "text": "This season's rising hotspot.",
    "start": 599.017,
    "duration": 2.361
  }
]